  "title": "Quantity Surveyor (Up to $3200 / 5 days / Pioneer)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Quantity Surveyor (ID8394)<br />Location: Pioneer, Singapore<br />Working Hour：Mon-Fri, 9am to 6pm<br />Salary: $2800 - 3200<br /><br />Job Description:<br />-To perform the full spectrum of duties required of as a quantity surveyor<br />-To be in control and responsible for the management of all contracts/sub-contracts activities including, meeting project budget, ensure profitability, terms and conditions of the contract/sub-contract, schedule procurement activities to meet projects deadline.<br />-To oversee, lead and manage the qs team for the overall direction, coordination, execution of the projects from tender development to inception of construction to final completion of the Projects.<br />-To oversee, lead and manage the purchase team for the overall direction, development to inception of construction to final completion of the project.<br /><br />Requirement:   <br />- At least 1 Years Quantity Surveyor Working Experience</p>",
